---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
const updated = 'June 21, 2026';
---

<Layout
  title="Terms of Service — revpdf"
  description="The terms that govern your use of the revpdf reader app and website."
>
  <article class="legal section">
    <a class="back" href="/">← Back to home</a>
    <h1>Terms of Service</h1>
    <p class="muted">Last updated: {updated}</p>

    <p>
      These Terms of Service (“Terms”) govern your use of the revpdf mobile application and the
      revpdf.in website (together, the “Service”). By using the Service you agree to these Terms. If
      you do not agree, please do not use the Service.
    </p>

    <h2>1. The app</h2>
    <p>
      revpdf is a document reader for Android. It reads files that you choose from your own device.
      The app works offline and does not require an account.
    </p>

    <h2>2. Your content</h2>
    <p>
      You are responsible for the documents you open with revpdf and for ensuring you have the right
      to access them. Your files, highlights and reading progress stay on your device — we never
      receive, upload or store them.
    </p>

    <h2>3. Acceptable use</h2>
    <p>
      You agree not to misuse the Service, including by attempting to reverse-engineer it for
      malicious purposes, redistributing it as your own, or using it to infringe the rights of
      others.
    </p>

    <h2>4. No warranty</h2>
    <p>
      The Service is provided “as is”, without warranties of any kind. We do not guarantee that every
      document will render perfectly or that the Service will be uninterrupted or error-free.
    </p>

    <h2>5. Limitation of liability</h2>
    <p>
      To the maximum extent permitted by law, revpdf and its author are not liable for any indirect,
      incidental or consequential damages arising from your use of the Service, including loss of
      data on your device.
    </p>

    <h2>6. Changes</h2>
    <p>
      We may update these Terms from time to time. Continued use of the Service after changes take
      effect constitutes acceptance of the revised Terms.
    </p>

    <h2>7. Contact</h2>
    <p>
      Questions about these Terms? Reach out via <a href="https://bksh.site">bksh.site</a>.
    </p>
  </article>
</Layout>

<style>
  .legal {
    max-width: 720px;
  }
  .back {
    display: inline-block;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
    font-weight: 500;
  }
  .legal h1 {
    font-size: clamp(32px, 5vw, 44px);
  }
  .legal h2 {
    font-size: 22px;
    margin-top: 32px;
  }
</style>
